      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. it captures that condescending tone well. can you expand on that? specifically, maybe have him describe their lack of 'intellectual capacity' or 'moral development' compared to Europeans, to really drive home why the explorer thinks they can't govern themselves. keep it in that same 19th-century formal style.",
